section.section:
The cabinet shall provide linkages only to the following organizations that publicly report quality and outcome measures on Kentucky providers:
The Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services;
The Agency for Healthcare Research and Quality;
The Joint Commission; and
Other organizations that publicly report relevant outcome data for Kentucky providers as determined by the Health Services Data Advisory Committee.

text.section:
Any report the cabinet disseminates or refers the public to shall:
Not include data for a provider whose caseload of patients is insufficient to make the data a reliable indicator of the provider's performance;
Meet the requirements of subsection (1)(c) of this section;
Clearly identify the sources of data used in the report and explain the analytical methods used in preparing the data included in the report; and
Explain any limitations of the data and how the data should be used by consumers.
